title: JRE REVIEW of 1309 with Naval Ravikant
description:
Naval is a brilliant man with a lot to share. This has to be one of the most enlightening podcasts I've ever heard. Joe gets in deep talking about everything with Naval and he drops knowledge bomb after knowledge bomb. I really loved reviewing this one and today I'm joined by long time Rogan fan Garrett.

 

 

Enjoy my review folks!
